[am_make=${MAKE-make}
cat > confinc << 'END'
am__doit:
	@echo this is the am__doit target
.PHONY: am__doit
END
# If we don't find an include directive, just comment out the code.
AC_MSG_CHECKING([for style of include used by $am_make])
am__include="#"

_am_result=none
# First try
